# Commit ONLY platform-tagged baselines (e.g. *-chromium-linux.png).
# Vitest writes failure artifacts (actual/diff images, *-N.png) next to the
# baselines on a mismatch; never commit those. Allowlist approach: ignore
# everything, then re-include directories + the .gitignore + baselines.
*
!*/
!.gitignore
!*-chromium-linux.png
